Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.46,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}ひとり雨宿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:28.01,ED_JP3,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}けど 空に罪はない
