Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:02.95,ED_CHT1,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我是无人察觉散发芬芳的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:05.16,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}我竭力地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.56,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}汲取水分呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:12.36,ED_CHT2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fade(100,150)}时而会欢笑时而会哭泣
